Maintainer: Brecht Devleesschauwer <Brecht.Devleesschauwer@UGent.be>
BugReports: https://github.com/brechtdv/QMRA/issues
Description: Parametric models for exposure assessment and dose-response assessment in QMRA. IMPORTANT: the Bayesian models in the QMRA package call on JAGS (Just Another Gibbs Sampler), which therefore has to be available on the user's system. JAGS can be downloaded from http://mcmc-jags.sourceforge.net/
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0), rjags, coda, methods, stats4
SystemRequirements: jags (>= 3.2.0)
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: http://users.ugent.be/~bdvleess/R/QMRA/
LazyData: yes